description.en:
FeedPups - $FUPS a charity-focused #DeFi & #GameFI project on #BinanceSmartChain 

Unique features:
NFT marketplace - We will have our own NFT marketplace, where you will not only be able to collect your favorite Feed Pups characters, they will be able to be used in game, to enhance the gaming experience. 

#GameFi Platform - Our #GameFi platform will feature a wide variety of games, such as platformer, multiplayer shooter, fantasy and adventure, RPG and turn based. This will attract a global audience within the gaming world

With all of this, we plan to End Hunger with our charities, when % of all transactions will go to feeding puppies and children alike.
